headline: 5th Palm Beach CorpGov Forum Highlights & Look Ahead
summary: The 5th Palm Beach CorpGov Forum took place on Nov. 5-6, 2025, featuring keynote speaker Josh Frank, Partner and Co-Chief Investment Officer at Wall Street legend Nelson Peltz’s Trian Fund Management. He was joined by other newsmakers including Daphna Edwards Ziman, who led the Project Rise effort to buy Paramount Global, now Paramount Skydance Corp.
